reviewText: if you were expecting something like animal instincts, for get it. it is like buying a box of your favorite cereal and you find out there is nothing in the box......bummer
Shannon Whirry is beautiful Actress with a great Body! the only reason I have this movie  (grin)

"Animal Instincts 2" doesn't quite measure up to the standard set by the first "Animal Instincts" (again, get the unrated VHS version; the DVD version has been substantially cut), but Shannon Whirry still puts your video system at serious risk of burnout whenever she appears on the screen!
